  <description><![CDATA[<p>A long time favourite with Inghams clients, the Lizard Creek Lodge offers top of the range accommodation, facilities and service in <a data-udi="umb://document/9516ae02f06047549f1709652a18a74d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9516ae02f06047549f1709652a18a74d}" title="Fernie">Fernie</a> Alpine Resort. Distinguished by its private setting just a few meters from the Elk quad chair lift making Lizard Creek Lodge superbly positioned for ski in and ski out convenience. The hotel has a great heated outdoor pool, whirlpool, health club, gift shop and ski equipment hire shop.</p>]]></description>
