  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>All have a living area with fireplace, balcony, TV, DVD/video, pay movies, full bathroom with hairdryer and full open-plan kitchen including dishwasher</li>
<li><strong>Studios </strong>(sleeping 1-2) Double sofa bed in the living area and small kitchenette<strong><br /></strong></li>
<li><strong>1 Bedroom Condo </strong>(sleeping 2) One bedroom with king size bed and living area with double sofa bed.</li>
<li><strong>1 Bedroom Condo + loft - </strong>(sleeping 2-6) Double sofa bed in the living area, one bedroom with king size bed, bath and WC; stairs leading to open loft with two queen size beds with shower and WC. </li>
<li><strong>2 Bedroom Condo - </strong>(sleeping 2-6) One bedroom with king size bed, second bedroom with two queen size beds and living area with double sofa bed.</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
